; BIND reverse data file for empty rfc1918 zone
;
; DO NOT EDIT THIS FILE - it is used for multiple zones.
; Instead, copy it, edit named.conf, and use that copy.
;
$TTL	86400
@	IN	SOA	dev.org. root.dev.org. (
			      2		; Serial
			 604800		; Refresh
			  86400		; Retry
			2419200		; Expire
			  86400 )	; Negative Cache TTL
;
@	IN	NS	proxyserver.dev.org.

10	IN	PTR	proxyserver.dev.org.
10	IN	PTR	www.dev.org.

; soc below
40	IN	PTR 	soc.dev.org.
